Northbridge College (CollegeWeb) — login reference (LOCAL COPY)
==============================================================
Copy this file to docs/LOGIN_CREDENTIALS.txt and fill in your values.
LOGIN_CREDENTIALS.txt is gitignored — do not commit real passwords.

Staff / admin portal (after running seed scripts)
-------------------------------------------------
Role           Username        Password        Permissions (summary)
Full admin     (your choice)   (your choice)   Full — holds, registration, future grade tools
Limited admin  (your choice)   (your choice)   Holds + registration add/drop; no grade import
Viewer         staff           (see seed_staff) Read-only — browse admin pages, no POST changes

Seed commands (from project root):
  php scripts/seed_superadmin.php <username> <password>
  php scripts/seed_limited_admin.php <username> <password>
  php scripts/seed_staff.php

Email OTP 2FA (staff sign-in)
-----------------------------
After username + password, staff must enter a 6-digit code emailed to the address on file.

Setup (once per environment):
  composer install
  php scripts/migrate.php
  cp app/config/2fa_config.php.example app/config/2fa_config.php
  Edit 2fa_config.php with your SMTP host, port, encryption (tls/ssl), username, password, from_email, from_name.

Staff email addresses live on auth_users.email. An admin sets them under Admin → Accounts → Email (2FA).

Where to sign in
----------------
Staff portal:     …/public/login.php
Verification:     …/public/verify_otp.php
Admin dashboard:  …/public/admin.php

